----------------
PST experiment for team LBI with high-speed camera. On the roof of the last bunker. Snow depth representative for this elevation. The layer of surface hoar is an oddity due to the close proximity of the creek.

PROFILE
-------
just a few cm of new snow and some settlement. The slab above the surface hoar is still very soft. The layer below the thick crust was very variable (hardness 1 to 3) and consisted of many ice chunks mixed with facets.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
no rutschblock.
PST 30 PP @ 31.5
propagated about halfway through the 3 meter long PST.

SNOW SURFACE
------------
foot penetration of about 60 cm

SNOW DRIFT
----------
nothing

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
tried to get slopes to whumpf close to the creak, but nothing happening even with snow shoes

AVALANCHES
----------
nothing observed</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2019-01-11T05:00:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2019-01-11T21:01:43+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2019-01-14T09:37:55+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos - Fluelabach - SLF windtunnel</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>1640</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>0</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.869968 46.807735</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">86.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-7.7</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">86.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">2.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>PP</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>1.0</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>1.5</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">2.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">4.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>PP</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>DF</caaml:grainFormSecond